going to apologize.<delay frames="40" /> <anim id="HappyDance" target="actor" targetSpec="" />Yeah, I am <delay20 />WAY<delay20 />
into this plan!<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" /></message>
	<message label="015" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><20_2 arg="3" /><anim id="QuestionMark" target="actor" targetSpec="" />Um<tag a="110" b="0" /><delay20 /> Did you say blow up? <delay20 />Hashtags
can do that?<delay frames="40" /> <anim id="Frantic" target="actor" targetSpec="" />I-I-I didn't know they
were THAT dangerous, <tag a="110" b="5" />!<anim id="EmotEnd" target="mainNpc" targetSpec="" /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="subNpc" targetSpec="" /></message>
	<message label="016" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><20_2 arg="7" /><20_2 arg="4" /><anim id="Eh" target="mainNpc" targetSpec="" /><anim id="SmugFace" target="actor" targetSpec="" />See, <tag a="110" b="31" arg="0xcd00" />? <delay frames="40" />Told you!<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="mainNpc" targetSpec="" /></message>
	<message label="017" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><20_2 arg="3" />Seriously, <tag a="110" b="3" />?<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" /></message>
	<message label="018" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><20_2 arg="4" /><anim id="Thinking" target="actor" targetSpec="" />Hmm<tag a="110" b="0" />but if <tag a="110" b="3" />'s
down with being stubborn,<20_2 arg="5" />
<delay20 />maybe the trend's peaking.<pageBreak /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />Yeah, this stubborn thing's old.<delay frames="40" /> <anim id="BigSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />I'll
apologize to my besties so we can
get front-row seats to the next trend!<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="mainNpc" targetSpec="" /></message>
	<message label="019" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><20_2 arg="6" /><anim id="OhGeez" target="actor" targetSpec="" />I have no clue what just happened.<anim id="Negative" target="player" targetSpec="" /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="player" targetSpec="" /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><pageBreak />Thanks<tag a="110" b="0" /><delay frames="40" />I think.<anim id="EmotEnd" target="mainNpc" targetSpec="" /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="subNpc" targetSpec="" /></message>
	<message label="020" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Shocked" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><tag a="50" b="3" /><tag a="110" b="3" />!<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" /></message>
	<message label="021" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><20_2 arg="4" /><anim id="TakenAback" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><delay20 />Huh? <delay20 />You don't <delay8 />CARE?!<20_2 arg="5" /><delay frames="40" /> <anim id="Frantic" target="actor" targetSpec="" />But if you
don't care, how am I supposed to
be trendy!<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" /></message>
	<message label="022" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><20_2 arg="3" /><anim id="ShyBoy" target="actor" targetSpec="" />Maybe not caring about trends is the
next hot trend, <tag a="110" b="5" />!<anim id="EmotEnd" target="mainNpc" targetSpec="" /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="subNpc" targetSpec="" /></message>
	<message label="101" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Explain" target="actor" targetSpec="" />No offense, but you don't seem like
the island type. <delay20 />Wouldn't you be
happier in a big city?<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" /></message>
	<message label="102" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />Humble roots are totes in right now.<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="HappyFlower" target="actor" targetSpec="" />I'm going make my big debut as an
island girl!<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" /></message>
	<message label="103" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="ShyBoy" target="actor" targetSpec="" />Are you sure <tag a="110" b="8" />'s
roots aren't a little TOO
humble for you?<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><pageBreak />Are island styles even trendy?<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" /></message>
	<message label="104" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Smiling" target="actor" targetSpec="" />Oh! <delay20 />I'm bringing <tag a="110" b="8" />
styles with me to the city!<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><pageBreak />It'll be just what my big hype
campaign needs!<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" /></message>
	<message label="105" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="QuestionMark" target="actor" targetSpec="" />Really? <delay20 />And how do you plan to
do that?<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" /></message>
	<message label="106" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="HappyDance" target="actor" targetSpec="" />We're going to make a magazine! <delay20 />I'm
going to show the world what a hot
spot <tag a="110" b="8" /> is!<anim id="EmotEnd" target="mainNpc" targetSpec="" /><pageBreak /><20_3 arg="8" /><anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />OK, <tag a="110" b="3" />,<20_2 arg="6" /><delay20 /> you're my
editor. <delay20 /><20_2 arg="7" /><anim id="BigSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><delay20 />And, <tag a="110" b="31" arg="0xcd00" />,
<anim id="Eh" target="mainNpc" targetSpec="" /><delay20 />you'll be my photographer.<anim id="EmotEnd" target="mainNpc" targetSpec="" /><pageBreak /><20_2 arg="8" />The first issue's going to be all about
<tag a="110" b="8" />'s most promising
young starlet<tag a="110" b="0" /><anim id="Dance" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><delay frames="60" />ME!<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="mainNpc" targetSpec="" /></message>
	<message label="107" attrib="00 00 01 00 00 00 00 00"><20_2 arg="6" /><anim id="Confused" target="actor" targetSpec="" />Wait, hang on. <delay20 /><tag a="50" b="3" /><tag a="110" b="3" />,
s-say something!<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="subNpc" targetSpec="" /></message>
	<message label="107_a" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Negative" target="actor" targetSpec="" />Nope! Not happening.<anim id="EmotEnd" target="mainNpc" targetSpec="" /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="subNpc" targetSpec="" /></message>
	<message label="107_b" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />Ready to be famous?<anim id="EmotEnd" target="mainNpc" targetSpec="" /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="subNpc" targetSpec="" /></message>
	<message label="108" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><20_2 arg="5" /><anim id="SadSpiral" target="subNpc" targetSpec="" /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />I'm with <tag a="110" b="3" />.<anim id="EmotEnd" target="subNpc" targetSpec="" /><pageBreak /><anim id="OhGeez" target="actor" targetSpec="" />Are you sure <tag a="110" b="8" /> even
wants all that attention?<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="subNpc" targetSpec="" /></message>
	<message label="109" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><20_2 arg="7" /><anim id="Confused" target="actor" targetSpec="" />But the hotels, <delay20 />the huge crowds, <delay20 />the
traffic, <delay20 />the premium housing prices!<delay frames="40" />
Who <delay8 />WOULDN'T<delay8 /> want that?<anim id="EmotEnd" target="mainNpc" targetSpec="" /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="subNpc" targetSpec="" /></message>
	<message label="110" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><20_2 arg="5" /><anim id="Negative" target="mainNpc" targetSpec="" /><anim id="HappyDance" target="actor" targetSpec="" />Yes, <delay8 />yes, <delay8 />yes! <delay20 />I can't wait!
<delay frames="40" />Make sure you get my glam
side, <tag a="110" b="31" arg="0xcd00" />!<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="mainNpc" targetSpec="" /></message>
	<message label="111" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="OhGeez" target="actor" targetSpec="" />Just so you know, the last time I
used a camera, all I got were blurry
pictures of my feet.<anim id="EmotEnd" target="mainNpc" targetSpec="" /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="subNpc" targetSpec="" /></message>
	<message label="201" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Explain" target="actor" targetSpec="" />But that's what I'm sayin'! <delay20 />Just
'cause <delay8 />YOU<delay8 /> say something's a hit
doesn't mean it is, <tag a="110" b="5" />!</message>
	<message label="202" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Aha" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><delay20 />Hang on! <delay20 />Did you just
say, <delay20 />"<tag a="110" b="5" />?"<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" /></message>
	<message label="203" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="OhGeez" target="actor" targetSpec="" />Uh, yeah, <delay20 />probably. <delay20 />I say
"<tag a="110" b="5" />" pretty much all the
time. <delay20 />So what, <tag a="110" b="5" />?<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="subNpc" targetSpec="" /></message>
	<message label="204" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="TakenAback" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><delay20 />SO WHAT?! <delay frames="40" />Isn't it totes obvious?<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="BigSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />"<tag a="50" b="3" /><tag a="110" b="5" />" is waaaay cooool!<pageBreak /><anim id="Frantic" target="actor" targetSpec="" />You have <delay20 />GOT<delay20 /> to let me say it!<delay frames="40" />
Pleeeeeeease! <delay20 /><tag a="50" b="3" /><tag a="110" b="5" />!<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" /></message>
	<message label="205" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />Well, it ain't like I can stop
you.<delay20 /> Sure, knock yourself
