	<message label="206" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="HappyDance" target="actor" targetSpec="" />Eeeeeeeeeeeeee! <delay frames="40" />So awesome!<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><pageBreak /><tag a="50" b="3" /><tag a="110" b="6" /> is totally going to
trend and go viral and be a hashtag
and EVERYTHING!<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><pageBreak />You and me, <delay20 />we'll be, like, <delay20 />the
Team #<capitaliseNextWord /><tag a="110" b="5" /> captains!<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" /></message>
	<message label="207" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Sighing" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><delay20 />It's just a silly phrase. <delay20 />I think you're
